{"tid":1254053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】劉曉明：港府已暫停修例　籲港人積極回應港府及特首 (08:08)","createTime":"2019-06-24T02:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T03:23:13.000Z","uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"88db1d0c837db06aa5fb25ef9c2243638b46f323","tid":1254053,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》爭議未息。中國駐英大使劉曉明上周五（21日）接受英國天空新聞台專訪時，再度就修例爭議發言，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲香港民眾積極回應港府及特首林鄭月娥。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉曉明稱，大多數英國媒體只關注上街的示威者，忘記了有80萬港人簽名支持修例。他續指出，港府已就修例徵求民眾意見和建議，在收到的4500份反饋中，有3000份支持修例，只有1500份反對。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明希望如今修例爭議的事態能夠平息，強調中央對港府有信心，而港府現已決定暫停修例，並花更多時間傾聽民眾聲音，呼籲港人積極回應港府和林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n他又反駁前港督彭定康的「修例破壞中英聯合聲明」言論，稱修例正是為了把香港建設成更美好地方，而非「避罪天堂」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190624/s00001/1561334605989/【逃犯條例】劉曉明-港府已暫停修例-籲港人積極回應港府及特首\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561334605989%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%98%8E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B7%B2%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8F%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=27beb5d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561334605989%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%98%8E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%B7%B2%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E7%B1%B2%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%8F%8A%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96&h=4898722a\" 